des:
A timeless fairy tale, lost in time, a sacred connection to Earth and Pristine, the unborn and formless embodiment of the natural. In this story the author describes his connection to this sacred space, the mystical daughter of pristine, he calls her Anoda, a Sioux connection to Earth. Can you find her in your child, the child of Earth? Of Pristine? In unconditional love?
This story has a take home message to end our predation of wildlife and forest trees.
A bridge to the world of passive flight, one with the Northern Winds.
You can return to the indigenous in you and take flight, escape to the woods near a residential air park, a pasture with a meaning, escape the Urban Madness and rediscover the sacred.
This skill has premium content on Air Parks and the Healing process, a naturalization to the sky and the space of ions, the heaven in us. Subscribe to plan your escape, and discover the Anoda in yourself.
 At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill. This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
